text: Jaime Cervantes Rivera (born 7 March 1955) is a Mexican politician from the Labor Party. From 2006 to 2009 he served as Deputy of the LX Legislature of the Mexican Congress representing Nayarit. ==References== Category:1955 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Nayarit Category:Members of the Chamber of Deputies (Mexico) Category:Labor Party (Mexico) politicians Category:21st-century Mexican politicians
